data.description: Excellent Opportunity To Become The Owner of This Three Bedroom One And One Half Bath Two Story Colonial.  There Is A Large Living Room, A Dining Room With French Doors Leading To The Screen Porch On The Back of The House With Two Ceiling Fans, Which Overlooks The Private Rear Yard.  The Back Yard Is Fences And Shrub Appointed.  The Eat-In-Kitchen Was Remodeled In 2003, The Roof Is Approximately 4 Years Old, The Hvac Is About Seven Years Old, The Hot Water Heater About 3 Years Old.  There Are Some Replacement Windows And A Pull Down Stairs For Attic Storage Access. The Property Is Centrally Located To Cherry Hill Mall, Moorestown Mall, Various Strip Malls, Fine Dining, Casual Dining, Various Bridges To Pennsylvania, Rt. 130, Rt. 73, Rt. 95, Rt. 295 And The New Jersey Turnpike.  To Complete The Recipe, It Just Needs You.
